</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/lit-lists/75-notable-translations-2023-michelle-johnson" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/NT23-Anchor.jpg?itok=n-DozcuZ" width="250" height="175" alt="The covers to ten books from the Notable Translations list below" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/lit-lists/75-notable-translations-2023-michelle-johnson">75 Notable Translations 2023
