</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-thumbnail"><div class="field-content imageleft">  <a href="/blog/translation/most-translated-authors-veronica-esposito" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/blog_thumbnail/public/EspositoAgatha-w.jpg?itok=mv-vaBPz" width="100" height="75" alt="A sepia-toned photograph of Agatha Christie" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-blog-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/most-translated-authors-veronica-esposito">The Most Translated Authors
</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">The Christie Archive Trust, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons<em>Who is the world’s most translated author? Agatha Christie? Antoine de Saint-…</em>
</div></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content date-display-single">December 11, 2024
</span></span>|<span><span class="field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/veronica-esposito" hreflang="en">Veronica Esposito</a>
